policy measure
which could

00:18:53.680 --> 00:18:56.440
save them from poverty.

00:18:56.440 --> 00:18:58.440
And I think, you know,
this is supported

00:18:58.440 --> 00:19:00.400
by ideas
like tax is wasted,

00:19:00.400 --> 00:19:03.280
like tax is corrupt,

00:19:03.280 --> 00:19:05.720
like tax goes
to a corrupt government.

00:19:05.720 --> 00:19:09.720
Taxing the rich can be
used to lower your taxes

00:19:09.720 --> 00:19:10.840
and that is the only way

00:19:10.840 --> 00:19:12.520
that you can get
your assets

00:19:12.520 --> 00:19:13.720
back from wealthy people.

00:19:13.720 --> 00:19:16.480
If we don't tax them,

00:19:16.480 --> 00:19:19.200
they will continue
to never sell any assets

00:19:19.200 --> 00:19:21.160
have enormous amounts
of passive income

00:19:21.160 --> 00:19:23.760
which they and their kids
will use to outcompete

00:19:23.760 --> 00:19:25.240
you and your kids
for the assets

00:19:25.240 --> 00:19:27.040
which you currently own
and in the end

00:19:27.040 --> 00:19:29.120
your family will own
nothing.

00:19:29.120 --> 00:19:31.840
So listen, tax for me
is...

00:19:31.840 --> 00:19:34.440
it's not about increasing
the size of government.

00:19:34.440 --> 00:19:35.200
It's not about more

00:19:35.200 --> 00:19:36.920
levels of government
spending.

00:19:36.920 --> 00:19:38.680
Tax for me
is about defending

00:19:38.680 --> 00:19:40.440
ordinary families

00:19:40.440 --> 00:19:42.600
from the growing power
and wealth of the rich.

00:19:42.600 --> 00:19:44.320
It's about getting wealth

00:19:44.320 --> 00:19:47.000
back into the
hands of ordinary people,

00:19:47.000 --> 00:19:48.760
and it's about making

00:19:48.760 --> 00:19:50.200
life better,
or at the very least

00:19:50.200 --> 00:19:52.320
stopping life
from getting worse.

00:19:52.320 --> 00:19:55.040
So to conclude,

00:19:55.040 --> 00:19:57.600
I would like to make
the clear point

00:19:57.600 --> 00:19:59.800
that the only way

00:19:59.800 --> 00:20:01.640
to reduce the tax burden

00:20:01.640 --> 00:20:04.720
for you, for ordinary
families like you,

00:20:04.720 --> 00:20:06.400
is to increase taxes.

00:20:06.400 --> 00:20:09.760
But to increase taxes on
the rich.

00:20:09.760 --> 00:20:11.080
We're going to campaign
for it.

00:20:11.080 --> 00:20:13.720
We're here every week.
Tell your friends.

00:20:13.720 --> 00:20:15.280
Tell your mum. Thank you.

